        <item>
            <title>1.11.1</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 20:23:29 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>36</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.11.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fix SSH remote session crash on launch after the Claude Code extension updated to 2.1.112 (`Fatal: ENOENT` / `native binary not found`)
- Fix `/resume` inside an SSH remote session falling back to a non-existent native binary
- Honor the launcher's "Continue session" toggle in SSH remote mode (previously ignored)
]]></description>
